{"tid":589461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"販民開口埋口就本土派","createTime":"2018-03-12T01:15:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-12T01:46:13.000Z","uid":156995,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ccef056f5c60fcb3a71f094ec1210f9b4c3c57f5","tid":589461,"uid":156995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:15:43.000Z","msg":"我心諗本乜春土派，根本DQ之後就已經徹底收咗皮<br />\n本土派嘅人唔係坐撚緊監就係比政權趕盡殺絕<br />\n淨返低嗰啲死淨種已經聲都唔出<br />\n都仲可以比你地拎出嚟鞭屍，做人唔好咁撚無恥好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喂你地班販民係中共政權認可嘅反對派，比你地入撚到圍去選都嬴唔到賴得邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fa86f069ed9de9132097811228f7ead421e8ea7","tid":589461,"uid":63909,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:22:30.000Z","msg":"販民廿幾年來從來唔會覺得自已錯架<br />\n自已係代表''民主''<br />\n所有野都係真理<br />\n只係一種宗教"},{"pid":"83115c8606a91d2fa20b81af3bb548602404a416","tid":589461,"uid":8858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:24:23.000Z","msg":"同又係佔中一樣啫"},{"pid":"80d3535646ee0253995a80d8a05b60fe117cc4ad","tid":589461,"uid":156995,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8fa86f069ed9de9132097811228f7ead421e8ea7","tid":589461,"uid":63909,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:22:30.000Z","msg":"販民廿幾年來從來唔會覺得自已錯架<br />\n自已係代表''民主''<br />\n所有野都係真理<br />\n只係一種宗教"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:26:11.000Z","msg":"成日自以為係民主代理人<br />\n其他人就係鬼係共產黨<br />\n用埋晒啲二元對立論屌人唔投佢即係投共<br />\n販民班撚樣永續反對派咁多年終於都有得懲罰下佢地"},{"pid":"9937d56552501189c40893bd4e502d735e75eceb","tid":589461,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:27:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/084237_74e818d7da05ecbe8e2e0a7ea708fdf9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F084237_74e818d7da05ecbe8e2e0a7ea708fdf9.png&h=6c9baf49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">多撚謝販民班大愛支（尤其民主党工党同社民狗！）囉！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啟德一早都知係港共專登設計既市區票倉膽！！！！</span></span></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<br />\n「姚松炎今次做選舉工程，同我哋傳統政黨，真係好唔同，我哋唔係好慣，尤其係打開地面戰嗰班，其實一直覺得佢危。<br />\n<br />\n我哋擺街站、洗樓、去屋邨，佢哋認為唔使做好多呢啲，覺得做好網上，網上反應熱烈，就好有信心。<br />\n<br />\n即使佢哋助選團，或者幫忙嘅團體開（街）站，但好似用錯力，星期五、六下晝，喺佐敦開站，我哋一般唔會咁做，因為嗰啲係街客，去行街，唔係選民；即使開喺住宅區，有啲朝早9點後先至開，嗰啲時間，人人返晒工，開站都無咩用。<br />\n<br />\n姚松炎團隊去土瓜灣少數族裔拉票，好奇怪，或者踩單車，我哋好多人睇到，暈低咁滯。或者係我哋太傳統，唔慣咁做。<br />\n<br />\n不過泛民好多大佬，就好buy佢呢套，所以一直覺得九西呢個位好易贏，無咩危機感，其實我地做開地區嘅，睇佢唔係咁穩陣。<br />\n<br />\n佢哋呢種選舉工程，喺比例代表制，效果可能會比較好，今次補選只係選一個位，未必可以咁打選戰。今次投票率咁低，有好多原因，如果唔諗點樣做，下次補選，我擔心唔容易贏。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/082155_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F082155_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=65e18a89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n</span></strong></span><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/082539_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F082539_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=e96c93c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"69be4037b9d3674c30700837067a19e4c51c488b","tid":589461,"uid":80814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:28:18.000Z","msg":"如果話屈婦人係咩都關佔中事，<br />\n泛民就係咩都關本土派 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c33a1cfb7824bb6d3671448cd885fc558b54593a","tid":589461,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:29:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">等睇泛民打手入嚟屈樓主五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"1743311caab9bae1cbee43ac5f002f2bbefbdebf","tid":589461,"uid":156995,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"69be4037b9d3674c30700837067a19e4c51c488b","tid":589461,"uid":80814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:28:18.000Z","msg":"如果話屈婦人係咩都關佔中事，<br />\n泛民就係咩都關本土派 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:32:27.000Z","msg":"搵啲唔存在嘅野嚟鞭屍，根本販民黃絲同屈婦人一擔擔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aec7ec90596dcf6fafcef52054072738a5bb5d23","tid":589461,"uid":156995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c33a1cfb7824bb6d3671448cd885fc558b54593a","tid":589461,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:29:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">等睇泛民打手入嚟屈樓主五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:34:01.000Z","msg":"屈囉，又唔會少忽肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我而家心情好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9614bdac94a5b89cc1fcc044fac8b8706f63f69f","tid":589461,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:34:35.000Z","msg":"香港 好多人吸開毒架嘛"},{"pid":"e57efc4667833d2d3c36e5561744e77e6fc0e884","tid":589461,"uid":156995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:46:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}